theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 24
text = "Listening: Irene, Charles, Annabeth, Dafne

Caller 01: I need to talk about something quite important with my sister. Well, important might not be the right word, but it’s definitely something she would like to know: we both always knew, deep down, that our neighbours were hiding something! 

Caller 02: I think my aunt has something to tell me, something that she should have told me while she was still with us. Our relationship was never the same after I married and started my own family, and this could be the chance to mend it.

"

